						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone lying in the temple of Siddhēśvara.</hi></p>						

						<p>Siṁghaṇa—A.D. 1228.</p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription referring to <hi rend="bold">Siṁgaṇadēva</hi> is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Sarvadhāri, Vai[śākha],</hi> Sunday. The <hi rend="italic">tithi</hi> is lost. The month <hi rend="bold">Vaiśākha</hi> in <hi rend="bold">Sarvadhāri</hi> corresponded to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1228, April-May.</hi> It records the death of a hero (name lost) of <hi rend="bold">Bēḍage</hi> (modern Byāḍgi), in a fight near <hi rend="bold">Kuṁchūr.</hi> </p>						

						</summary>
